data.description: Fantastic price for a 4 Bedroom home South of I-10. Freshly painted and brand new Luxury vinyl plank throughout the home make this an easy move in. Bring your toothbrush! The fenced in backyard and mature trees make you feel at home right away. New Roof 2020, LVP Flooring 8/2023, freshly painted 8/2023, Hot water heater 11/2019, AC & handler 2021. Entering the home you are greeted with an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings & sweeping views of the backyard. Great home for entertaining! The 4th Bedroom is the only thing on the 2nd flman cave, oor which makes it a private retreat, theater room, den or teen bedroom. All 4 bedrooms have walk-in closets. The 2-car garage features built in workshop with attic above. The backyard is completely fenced in with mature trees & a screened porch bases (Eglin AFB, 7th Special Forces, Hurlburt Field, top rated Destin beaches & just minutes to shopping & golfing. Schedule your private showing today!
